{"tid":1972963,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Lady Gaga今個星期日搞全球義唱 有eason同張學友份","createTime":"2020-04-15T00:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T11:13:38.000Z","uid":309002,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"94bc8a3f8be1ffab23062109c909215011a30b92","tid":1972963,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T00:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S8Qc2AS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS8Qc2AS.jpg&h=430033e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nfrom music picks fb<br />\nLady Gaga牽頭的全球義唱活動，香港時間星期日早上八時舉行。根據官方網站，香港的指定播放平台是JOOX以及收費台BEIN，其中JOOX的播放時間寫上TBA。全球播放平台就包括Facebook，IG，twitter及YouTube等大型社交平台。<br />\n在合作名單上，有兩個香港人的名字，分別是陳奕迅Eason Chan及張學友Jacky Cheung。以中國有多個媒體同時播放的情況來看，兩位香港人到時應該唱國語歌，而且好大機會是剛剛播出那兩首抗疫打氣歌。但作為一個香港人，希望他們能唱廣東歌，他倆有太多歌都比那兩首高班幾倍。<br />\nBy the way，大陸唔係封殺Lady Gaga咩？Gaga可唔可以到時講兩句希望達賴喇嘛為大家祈願抗疫？<br />\n<br />\n'One World: Together At Home' official website<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.globalcitizen.org/en/connect/togetherathome/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalcitizen.org%2Fen%2Fconnect%2Ftogetherathome%2F&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=8e8719c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.globalcitizen.org/en/connect/togetherathome/</a><br />\n<br />\n陣容好鼎盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟香港代表唱廣東歌定國語抗疫歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d8566d4f0e0fec1432e457871b8b24eb6a3854","tid":1972963,"uid":309002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T01:03:34.000Z","msg":"究竟佢地會唱廣東歌定國語歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce040b79e6f3f79f12516021e012825b3ba4cd88","tid":1972963,"uid":199565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T01:58:42.000Z","msg":"識唱一定唱愛國抗疫歌，不如重溫下先<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1969463/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\